{"tid":1876411,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人成功說服屋企人養寵物","createTime":"2020-02-12T11:21:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-22T10:17:12.000Z","uid":135115,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"9ecc69f3a900fb8580c8a408a419ecda4e5b4202","tid":1876411,"uid":135115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T11:21:24.000Z","msg":"一直都好鍾意貓<br />\n最近見到一隻好合眼緣嘅貓<br />\n好想帶佢返屋企<br />\n但屋企人都唔鍾意動物<br />\n我見過隻貓幾次已經開始有感情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本身打算先斬後奏<br />\n但我怕會影響大家感情<br />\n有冇人有類似經驗而成功養到架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"153c4f32cd708a6a8d411af56ab0736ceb2a5e52","tid":1876411,"uid":163734,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T11:26:12.000Z","msg":"我之前係街上面執咗隻貓，然後拎咗返屋企，呃屋企人話已經放咗上網等人領養。一個星期之後，就變咗係我老竇老母湊隻貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a38c18d9556a6f7cc0c7c906ff6821c4cdd743a","tid":1876411,"uid":163734,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"153c4f32cd708a6a8d411af56ab0736ceb2a5e52","tid":1876411,"uid":163734,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T11:26:12.000Z","msg":"我之前係街上面執咗隻貓，然後拎咗返屋企，呃屋企人話已經放咗上網等人領養。一個星期之後，就變咗係我老竇老母湊隻貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T11:26:33.000Z","msg":"而家已經養咗4年"},{"pid":"98ed077d7b9778dc3c2ea0c98fe04a9ef7d9aad9","tid":1876411,"uid":235277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T11:27