"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T11:46:00.000Z","msg":"呀媽自稱貓毛敏感<br />\n唔畀我養貓<br />\n我帶咗返去無耐<br />\n呀媽每日返到屋企都問貓貓喺邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3de0526bb7a62ca2bd7fb8164e9db1d037b9f01","tid":1876411,"uid":135115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T12:27:26.000Z","msg":"我探口風時我媽成日話會襯我唔喺屋企掉咗佢<br />\n我好驚佢真係咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又驚拎咗隻貓返去<br />\n佢地唔錫隻貓<br />\n對隻貓都唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ede2e9bccda0d922ea89f60ce87c8e6fa1501dc","tid":1876411,"uid":63426,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T12:44:05.000Z","msg":"千祈唔好先斬後奏，咁樣你會無左個老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都係先斬後奏，頭2星期我老母日日都嘈叫我比返隻貓人地。<br />\n後來隻貓變左做佢個仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我老母重成日手作紙皮箱屋仔/ 床比隻貓<br />\n日日同隻貓講野，本身電話從來都唔影相<br />\n宜家日撚日都影隻貓<br />\n仆街我先係親生嫁"},{"pid":"44b507807e306d7c077c563f8ec79f033ac4a248","tid":1876411,"uid":1022,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"e3de0526bb7a62ca2bd7fb8164e9db1d037b9f01","tid":1876411,"uid":135115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T12:27:26.000Z","msg":"我探口風時我媽成日話會襯我唔喺屋企掉咗佢<br />\n我好驚佢真係咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又驚拎咗隻貓返去<br />\n佢地唔錫隻貓<br />\n對隻貓都唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T12:58:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53a906fb49ca706254363f968d80d6627f012e31","tid":1876411,"uid":304619,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T13:17:32.000Z","msg":"帶左翻去先 分分鐘過一排你乜地位都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c62694aca0d2c467d10abc1a65c52e8fa129e384","tid":1876411,"uid":135115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T13:28:28.000Z","msg":"頭先成功說服咗我媽<br />\n但佢話要過埋我啊爸嗰關<br />\n但我爸係極討厭動物<br />\n仲係藍絲藍到黑<br />\n份人好文塞<br />\n又大男人<br />\n可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29953bb263ed531c6485f233e6d4cdef33defbd6","tid":1876411,"uid":42123,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T13:52:13.000Z","msg":"藍絲分析唔到<br />\n不過我老母本身話唔養，又嫌臭又盛<br />\ne家，叫我行開d唔好阻隻貓訓覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nd閪貓有超能力<br />\n前提係隻貓唔好有病/ 唔會太惡"},{"pid":"ec8e1bc08532004b05f3e5c8361647c41b22a26f","tid":1876411,"uid":259973,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"9ecc69f3a900fb8580c8a408a419ecda4e5b4202","tid":1876411,"uid":135115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T11:21:24.000Z","msg":"一直都好鍾意貓<br />\n最近見到一隻好合眼緣嘅貓<br />\n好想帶佢返屋企<br />\n但屋企人都唔鍾意動物<br />\n我見過隻貓幾次已經開始有感情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本身打算先斬後奏<br />\n但我怕會影響大家感情<br />\n有冇人有類似經驗而成功養到架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T15:28:28.000Z","msg":"洗西你說服咩，拎返去一個月，你就成會屋企最底層嘅生物啦<br />\n一個月後：<br />\n你老母：你死開啲唔好整到隻貓<br />\n你老豆：好心你出多啲錢買啲好少少嘅罐罐啦？你？咁撚大個食白飯得啦啦，食咩食"},{"pid":"1af06455c6198e139ed5f260b6ecc1f0ef3f9c0f","tid":1876411,"uid":245523,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T00:11:49.000Z","msg":"我勸你唔好聽上面啲人講先斬後奏 失敗案例冇人會分享<br />\n唔鐘意就係唔鐘意 初頭可能會睇在你份上對隻野隻眼開隻眼閉 但狗會吠貓會叫 人寵相處唔夾唔到 你點肯定你屋企人唔會趁你唔係度掉咗佢？或者虐待佢？<br />\n我就係有朋友夾硬養貓 養咗一陣之後佢阿爸喺佢岀咗去嘅時候掉咗落街市 從此就搵唔返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8917b04298b05579aeb4f17619d3100a30f64a43","tid":1876411,"uid":135115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1af06455c6198e139ed5f260b6ecc1f0ef3f9c0f","tid":1876411,"uid":245523,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T00:11:49.000Z","msg":"我勸你唔好聽上面啲人講先斬後奏 失敗案例冇人會分享<br />\n唔鐘意就係唔鐘意 初頭可能會睇在你份上對隻野隻眼開隻眼閉 但狗會吠貓會叫 人寵相處唔夾唔到 你點肯定你屋企人唔會趁你唔係度掉咗佢？或者虐待佢？<br />\n我就係有朋友夾硬養貓 養咗一陣之後佢阿爸喺佢岀咗去嘅時候掉咗落街市 從此就搵唔返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T04:43:26.000Z","msg":"我就係擔心呢樣<br />\n我爸真係冇乜同理心嗰啲來<br />\n佢乜都做得出<br />\n但我又諗唔到咩方法氹掂佢<br />\n我唔奢求佢好錫隻貓<br />\n但起碼唔好對佢差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26b8f50c0c0a410b37c535232196846028728453","tid":1876411,"uid":135354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T06:22:18.000Z","msg":"我前幾日都問完屋企人 佢哋話唔俾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n已經放棄咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0da4052c95d04ad636102ddf2c8c1bb1a7c014d1","tid":1876411,"uid":248670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"153c4f32cd708a6a8d411af56ab0736ceb2a5e52","tid":1876411,"uid":163734,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T11:26:12.000Z","msg":"我之前係街上面執咗隻貓，然後拎咗返屋企，呃屋企人話已經放咗上網等人領養。一個星期之後，就變咗係我老竇老母湊隻貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T06:25:15.000Z","msg":"有料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f267db8a0ec7655f2111a28137d1bd3974b518b5","tid":1876411,"uid":98498,"like":0,"disli